Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.00,0:04:21.14,English,,0,0,0,,so I showed visual learners pictures of 10 items,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.14,0:04:25.49,Chinese,,0,0,0,,但是对于另一部分的视觉学习者 我则是把这些东西读出来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.14,0:04:25.49,English,,0,0,0,,but for other visual learners I read out the items instead.
